org.gridgain.grid.typedef
Class G

java.lang.Object
  org.gridgain.grid.GridFactory
      org.gridgain.grid.typedef.G

public class G
extends GridFactory

Defines alias for GridFactory by extending it. Since Java doesn't provide type aliases (like Scala, for example) we resort to these types of measures. This is intended to provide for more concise code in cases when readability won't be sacrificed. For more information see GridFactory.
